{"word":"G4062 - περιτρέπω - peritrépō - per-ee-trep'-o - + make mad","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιτρέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>peritrépō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-trep'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>+ make mad"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயித்தியமுண்டாக்கு, திருப்பு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to turn about to turn; to transfer or change by turning"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>turn around</i>, that is, (mentally) to <i>craze:</i> - + make mad."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}